Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.35,Default,Kirasaka,0,0,0,,The bath feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:16.07,Default,Kirasaka,0,0,0,,It feels great to travel by ship once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:19.42,Default,Kirasaka,0,0,0,,It would have been amazing if it wasn't a trip for work, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:22.02,Default,Grenda,0,0,0,,{\an8}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:23.85,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Wait, Grenda! You need rinse off the shampoo properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:25.10,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:31.15,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! Are you okay!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.80,Default,Kirasaka,0,0,0,,Come on, do you really think I'd be fine after something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:37.40,Default,Kirasaka,0,0,0,,Hang on, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:39.97,Default,Yuiri,0,0,0,,Kirasaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:42.90,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,Yuiri, what's wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:44.00,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,Is Grenda—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:45.92,Default,Kirasaka,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:48.05,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,Why are you here, Kirasaka!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:50.17,Default,Kirasaka,0,0,0,,I should be asking you the same thing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:53.12,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,The two of us are on a mission, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:56.10,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,We're here to guard that girl until she reaches Itogami Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:57.32,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:01.97,Default,Kirasaka,0,0,0,,I'm on a scouting mission for the MAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:05.80,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,MAR? The multinational sorcery corporation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:09.77,Default,Kirasaka,0,0,0,,What was that impact just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:11.87,Default,Shio,0,0,0,,Hang on, did we run aground?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:13.20,Default,Grenda,0,0,0,,Yuiri, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:15.60,Default,Grenda,0,0,0,,Many ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.17,0:01:27.42,Default,Kirasa,0,0,0,,What on earth...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:33.87,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The name of that city was Itogami Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:41.75,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,An artificial island floating on the Pacific Ocean, made from carbon fiber, resin, metal, and magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:50.17,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The Special Magical District. A certain boy lived in that city that was built to shelter demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:56.97,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The Fourth Progenitor. A fourth progenitor who was never supposed to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:05.07,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,A future emperor, who would someday carve out his own empire and reign over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:09.45,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,His name is Akatsuki Kojou!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.07,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Ugh, I feel like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:50.05,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I just got back from the mainland, and I already have school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:10.42,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Oh, Kojou-kun. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:15.22,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Actually, put on some clothes already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:18.75,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Walking around naked in front of a teenage girl is a crime, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:19.67,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:22.77,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Geez. If you're looking for your shirt, it's on the dining table chair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.95,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get dressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:27.62,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Fine, fine. You should do that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.77,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,D-Did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:34.12,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Huh? We're out of milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.50,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,No reaction!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:40.40,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I used up the last of the milk to make scrambled eggs earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.30,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Seriously? I was looking forward to drinking some.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:47.12,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Oh well. I guess I'll go buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.72,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I just hope the shops received their stock for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:55.35,Signs,SIGNS,0,0,0,,{\frz351.3\pos(513.143,568.857)}Logistics take a big hit due to successive cancellations of cargo ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:55.07,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, there as some accident involving cargo ships, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:57.77,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,It's been happening a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:01.05,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, fresh foodstuffs go out of stock so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.35,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Not much we can do about that. This is an artificial island, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:07.95,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I'll hit up a few stores on my way back from school with Himeragi and search for some.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:13.72,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,You're... walking back with Yukina-chan again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.75,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hmm? Why shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:19.35,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,N-No! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:27.30,Default,Yukia,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:30.92,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,She's been acting strangely ever since we got back from the mainland.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:33.75,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I can't really explain it well, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:38.77,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,She went through a lot back then, so she might still be in shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:43.05,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,A lot of stuff did happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:45.42,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Even Asagi finally found out about my secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:47.92,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,That reminds me, is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:52.52,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,More or less. She interrogated me non-stop on our way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.87,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I ended up having to tell her everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:06:01.10,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I had to tell her about you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:05.37,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,So I told her about the Lion King Organization and stuff... Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:10.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I don't think so. I've received permission to reveal my identity based on the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:17.85,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I see. I explained to her that you're stuck with me because that's your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,"Stuck with you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:25.00,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong, Himeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.15,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai, you're really insensitive, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:29.55,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I already knew that, but still.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:32.67,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Huh? Himeragi! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:41.62,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,What the hell? Both Nagisa and Himeragi are acting weird early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:44.22,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Good morning, Fourth Progenitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:45.85,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:47.72,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.07,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.52,Default,Rin,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:55.67,Default,Rin,0,0,0,,I see the two of you already have a weird mood going right from the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:56.80,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Hi there, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:07:00.82,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,W-We don't really have a weird mood or anything. Right, Asagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.25,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,T-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:07.37,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,The two of us just got back from the mainland, so we're tired. In more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.90,Default,Rin,0,0,0,,Eh? The two of you went to the mainland? Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:12.57,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Kojou, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:14.12,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,That's not what he meant, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:16.82,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,It's not what you're thinking at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.12,Default,Rin,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:19.55,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,'Sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.97,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,What're you guys fighting about so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.30,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:25.65,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:29.02,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Here you go, a souvenir from Tokyo. Hope you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.50,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Oh, you went to the mainland as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.87,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Well, a lot of stuff happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:36.80,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:42.20,Default,Rin,0,0,0,,Well, I'm just glad all three of you came back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.45,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Safely?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:47.05,Default,Rin,0,0,0,,Akatsuki-kun, didn't you notice anything after seeing this classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:53.42,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it... an awful lot of people seem to be running late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.52,Default,Rin,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:08:00.75,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,All the ships that were headed to Itogami Island ran into accidents, ran aground, or the passengers had food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.95,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Not a single ship has arrived here since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.50,Default,Rin,0,0,0,,Even the flights are grounded due to turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.60,Default,Rin,0,0,0,,That's why we're in such a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:09.72,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:10.75,Default,Rin,0,0,0,,Very.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:13.00,Default,Rin,0,0,0,,That's one hell of a coincidence, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.62,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,A coincidence, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:17.58,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,I hope that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.11,Signs,SIGNS,0,0,0,,{\pos(1028,104)}This machine is in working order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.11,Signs,SIGNS,0,0,0,,{\pos(303,121)}Apologies for the inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.11,Signs,SIGNS,0,0,0,,{\pos(485,210)}Due to the cancellation of cargo ships, we have not received fresh stocks of food
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.11,Signs,SIGNS,0,0,0,,{\pos(291,306)}and hence the menu is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.32,Default,girl1,0,0,0,,Hey, Yukina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.77,Default,girl1,0,0,0,,I heard that the two of you went to the mainland during the winter holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.07,Default,girl1,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.42,Default,girl1,0,0,0,,She's not acting like herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.10,Default,girl1,0,0,0,,She was spacing out during class, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:00.95,Default,girl1,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like she's sick or anything, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.17,Default,girl2,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.40,Default,girl2,0,0,0,,Maybe she's feeling down because they didn't have the Crab Cream Croquet that she usually eats?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.92,Default,girl1,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.47,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:26.57,Default,girl2,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:30.90,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Huh? Why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:34.17,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.35,Default,girl2,0,0,0,,Is she jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:38.52,Default,girl1,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:42.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,There you are, transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.70,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,So, Natsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:55.50,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,What the heck is up with these chains?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:10:00.05,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Show some respect when you're addressing a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:04.62,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's what you get for trying to run away the moment you saw my face, even though I spoke to you so kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:07.55,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,That's... Well, that was a reflex.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.87,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,My instincts screamed for me to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:11.87,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,After all that happened during during the New Year...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:16.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,New Year? I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:20.90,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:23.72,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,If that's how you want to play it then it's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.70,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,More importantly, let's get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.02,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Astarte, show them the documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:29.40,Default,Astarte,0,0,0,,Accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.27,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,This is—!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.75,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,The accident at sea that took place yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:39.50,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,The one that caused all sea trips to Itogami Island to be cancelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:46.12,Default,Astarte,0,0,0,,Negative. There are all reports of accidents that occurred between early morning and noon today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:47.60,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,So many!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:48.47,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:51.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We have already received reports of twenty one cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:52.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:11:00.42,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,No matter how many times we go over the data, the only thing all the ships had in common was that their destination was Itogami Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:07.65,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,However, because of these accidents, no people or goods have arrived at the island for the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:12.82,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,In other words, Itogami Island is effectively isolated at present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:15.50,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I had no idea the situation was so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:21.10,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I think I understand why you restrained Akatsuki-senpai, Minamiya-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:25.75,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Do you suspect that this abnormal situation is Senpai's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:29.05,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,In a nutshell, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:31.02,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Huh!? Why the hell would you think that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:36.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,It is likely that this incident is being caused by a magical barrier of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:42.65,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And the only ones with enough magical energy to pull that off are the vampire progenitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:46.37,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I thought the incident would be resolved once you were captured, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:50.32,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It wasn't me! You're doing this on purpose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:55.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Well then, on the off-chance that Akatsuki Kojou is not the cause—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:59.40,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You're still not convinced!? Actually, just get these chains off of me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:03.77,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Transfer student. What is your opinion, as an expert on magical terrorism?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:08.65,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Do you have any knowledge of sorcery that could build a barrier of this scale?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:13.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,The only method that would have a chance would be to use Feng Shui.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:19.22,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,While the forerunner of Feng Shui, the Shikisen technique, was used for fortune telling,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:21.32,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,it was also a large-scale sorcery technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:26.00,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Especially the Houkimon technique, which was developed for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:31.15,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,It was a large-scale military magic that was used to control the weather and rule over the lives of soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.42,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Military magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:34.67,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:36.62,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:40.57,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,If someone used the ley lines around this area to construct an Eight Trigams formation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:44.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,creating the current scenario is not impossible, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,That's right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:53.25,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I have no idea if there is a practitioner who is able to maintain a technique of this scale while avoiding detection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:58.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,After hearing you say that, I remembered a single incident that was similar to this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:02.65,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The destruction of the Special Magical District in Iroise, Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.20,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Iroise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:09.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Wasn't that the Special Magical District in the Atlantic Ocean that was abandoned six years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:13.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,From what I heard, that was caused by flooding due to accidents and storms...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.50,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That was the official explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,However, the actual reason was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:22.42,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The destruction of that city was a deliberate act.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.22,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,By Tartaros Lapus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:44.47,Default,December,0,0,0,,Carly, the target is moving along the estimated route by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.15,Default,December,0,0,0,,He'll be arriving shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:48.75,Default,Carly,0,0,0,,This is Carly. I have visual confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:50.77,Default,Carly,0,0,0,,Preparing to snipe the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:54.37,Default,December,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to you. Use your judgment and get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.87,Default,Carly,0,0,0,,Copy that. Thank you, December.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:59.35,Default,December,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:12.82,Default,Carly,0,0,0,,Confirmed hit. Moving on to the next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:18.10,Default,December,0,0,0,,If you take too long, the security will tighten. Get it done quickly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:21.80,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Tartaros Lapus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:26.50,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. They are a destructive group who carry out magical terrorism in exchange for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:33.12,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,One of its ringleaders was praised as a genius in the use of Feng Shui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:39.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Do you know the identity of that Feng Shui practitioner, Minamiya-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:43.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Senga Takehito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:46.75,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,He should be around forty years old now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,He is one of the leading Houkimon users in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:55.35,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,So if we find and capture him, we can break this Eight Trigams formation thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:58.00,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Theoretically, that would be the case, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:08.10,Default,Astarte,0,0,0,,Master. Emergency communication from the Island Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:13.50,Default,Astarte,0,0,0,,A Code Orange alert has been issued to all attack mages affiliated with the Artifical Island Management Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:15.82,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Orange!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:19.25,Default,Astarte,0,0,0,,It appears that one of the senior directors of the Corporation was killed by a sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:24.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,So they're looking to throw the chain of command into chaos?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:27.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Looks like it's definite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:28.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,This is a terrorist attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:32.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,They are planning to throw Itogami Island into chaos and destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:42.05,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,That's right. Hurry up and find out the identity of the sniper and the location from where the bullet was fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:45.27,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Also, assign security teams to guard all the senior directors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:50.72,Default,guy1,0,0,0,,Chief, there have been two new reports of accidents involving airplanes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.42,Default,guy2,0,0,0,,We have additional reports of accidents at sea as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:57.85,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,At this point, there is no more doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.77,Default,lady,0,0,0,,Large-scale magical terrorism, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:03.72,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,What's all the fuss about, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:09.67,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,President Yaze. My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:15.60,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,If the leaders of the organization become unsteady, the command at the lower levels will be disrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:18.60,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,Carry out your tasks with composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.30,Default,chief,0,0,0,,Where are you headed, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:29.05,Default,secretary,0,0,0,,After a meeting with Councillor Hashimura, he is slated to attend a commemoration ceremony for the Magical Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:30.90,Default,chief,0,0,0,,But the situation is—!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:36.62,Default,Yaze,0,0,0,,Do you expect me to cower in terror behind bamboo blinds, hiding from a mere assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:40.47,Default,chief,0,0,0,,I will arrange for additional security.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:42.45,Default,chief,0,0,0,,Please exercise caution at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:53.22,Default,lady,0,0,0,,Chief, Attack Mage Minamiya has sent an important report.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:56.20,Default,chief,0,0,0,,The Witch of the Void, huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:03.87,Default,chief,0,0,0,,Tartaros Lapus!? Why didn't the attack mage division realize it at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.55,Default,lady,0,0,0,,The related information is designated as top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.62,Default,lady,0,0,0,,Ordinary investigators do not have the clearance to access it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.55,Default,chief,0,0,0,,Make the preparations to declassify that information at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.20,Default,chief,0,0,0,,After that, contact the Lion King Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:19.15,Default,chief,0,0,0,,They are supposed to have an agent on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.37,Default,chief,0,0,0,,Do whatever it takes to obtain their cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:22.55,Default,lady,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:31.87,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:35.40,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,At this rate, I can't even look Kojou-kun in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:40.87,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I can't keep from staring at him, and my heart beats wildly when he so much as looks at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:45.92,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,My heart hurts so badly when I just see him with another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:50.10,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Are... these feelings real?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:55.07,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I can't talk to anyone about something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:01.67,Default,December,0,0,0,,Want some? Ice cream from Ruruya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:02.80,Default,December,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:05.55,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Huh? Umm... You are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:06.87,Default,December,0,0,0,,December.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.97,Default,December,0,0,0,,December. That's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:13.62,Default,December,0,0,0,,I'm fond of it. I'd like it if you called me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:20.00,Default,December,0,0,0,,I knew she was still around...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but to think I'd end up meeting her in such a manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.52,Default,December,0,0,0,,Well, I guess this is also a kind of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:29.82,Default,December,0,0,0,,I guess we're both going through some rough times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.72,Default,December,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:37.95,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Umm.. What are you doing here, December-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.80,Default,December,0,0,0,,Me? I'm here for surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:45.77,Default,December,0,0,0,,I told her that I had her back, but she said she didn't need any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:50.05,Default,December,0,0,0,,So I decided to just watch from afar while eating some ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:53.20,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,You're here to look at the Keystone Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.77,Default,December,0,0,0,,No, that's not quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:58.85,Default,December,0,0,0,,I'm here to see the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:02.97,Default,December,0,0,0,,The beginning of the end of the Special Magical District.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:10.17,Default,chief,0,0,0,,What was that vibration just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:13.40,Default,lady,0,0,0,,There appears to have been an explosion in the third underground parking garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:15.07,Default,chief,0,0,0,,An explosion!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:15.97,Default,dude1,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:20.30,Default,dude1,0,0,0,,Chairman Yaze Akishige's car is located in the third underground parking garage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:25.67,Default,lady,0,0,0,,President Yaze's vital signs signal has been cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.47,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,The Keystone Gate—!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.05,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:48.05,Default,December,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:50.95,Default,December,0,0,0,,Everything's fine. You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:54.15,Default,December,0,0,0,,This is my war, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:00.80,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,You... Why, after all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:07.60,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Please, return to your slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:20.80,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,That is our wish as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:25.17,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Terrorists set off an explosion!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.00,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "missing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.17,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Are you telling me that he was caught up in something like that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:32.10,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Bro, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:33.32,Default,chief,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:36.95,Default,chief,0,0,0,,Things are still in a chaos over here, so I don't have any more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:39.32,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Let me help with the search!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:41.67,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,With my power, I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:43.75,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:49.62,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yaze...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:54.72,Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,This is an announcement to all students.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:57.22,Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,Today's lessons have been canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.52,Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,All students are to return home immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:06.05,Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,{\an8}Repeat, today's lessons have been cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.20,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hey, Yaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:03.37,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:07.65,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,He must be shocked after hearing about the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:11.70,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yaze's father is an important person in the island's administration after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.02,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Tartaros Lapus, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.85,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I guess I can't just sit back and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.50,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Tartar sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.12,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Kojou, do you know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:21.95,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:24.77,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,You better not be hiding something from me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:29.15,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:35.05,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,So basically, the explosion that Motoki's father appears to have gotten mixed up in
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:38.30,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,and the reason why the ships have stopped arriving at the island are all the fault of this Tartar?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:40.27,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Tartaros Lapus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:43.52,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Natsuki-chan is after a Feng Shui practitioner called Senga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:47.10,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Right now, he's the only confirmed member that we know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:50.37,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,If you knew that, you should have told me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:51.80,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Do you think you can find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:53.77,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,I'll find him for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:21:59.32,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:01.85,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Himeragi? Why are you in the high school building?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:07.27,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,It's Nagisa-chan. She ran off somewhere by herself during lunch and hasn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:10.35,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,She hasn't responded to my messages either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:11.37,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Asagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:15.30,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Alright, fine. Let me find her before we start searching for the terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:18.85,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,No way... How can this be happening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:21.30,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Out of my way, Kojou!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.07,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Dammit, they got me. Now I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:28.42,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,A-Asagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:33.57,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Someone was hacking into my system. The Island Guard's network has been infected with a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.75,0:22:35.47,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's a powerful, military-grade virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:39.80,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't that pretty bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:45.27,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Of course it's bad. Like we didn't have enough problems with the chain of command being thrown into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:47.62,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai, maybe that is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:49.80,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Tartaros Lapus, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:54.87,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Where the heck is Nagisa wandering around at a time like this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:03.17,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Did you drag an unrelated civilian into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:05.12,Default,December,0,0,0,,Takehito.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:09.17,Default,December,0,0,0,,This girl just got a fright after seeing the explosion and fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.60,0:23:12.05,Default,December,0,0,0,,I can't leave a cute girl like her lying around, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.17,0:23:14.10,Default,December,0,0,0,,She might get kidnapped by some shady people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:18.35,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,That way you put it, it sounds like you're saying that we're not shady people ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:21.50,Default,December,0,0,0,,Are you okay with this, Takehito?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.60,0:23:24.42,Default,December,0,0,0,,You are not exactly unrelated to this island, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.07,0:23:29.37,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,That is exactly why there are some things that I cannot forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:32.37,Default,December,0,0,0,,I see. I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.92,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going to put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:38.05,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Using the Roses of Tartarus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:48.75,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Huh? What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:54.57,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! You didn't have to let me sleep on your lap—!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.67,0:23:55.57,Default,December,0,0,0,,Phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:58.20,Default,December,0,0,0,,It's ringing. Your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:23:59.40,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.35,0:24:03.00,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Kojou-kun? Why is he calling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:05.55,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,That freaking Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.85,0:24:09.40,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,"The weather was so good that I guess I fell asleep."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.82,0:24:11.10,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,What the hell!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:12.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I'm just glad she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.90,0:24:15.00,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:18.45,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Still, everyone seems pretty calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.55,0:24:23.52,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,People who live in the Special Magical District are used to disturbances of this level, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.72,0:24:31.42,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I just hope Asagi or Mogwai are able to find Senga before things get any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.52,0:24:33.77,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.17,0:24:36.27,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kojou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.05,0:24:39.72,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Thanks for giving me a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.05,0:24:41.35,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.55,0:24:43.75,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hey, Nagisa. Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.95,0:24:48.27,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Umm... I met her in the park, and she gave me a ride here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.75,0:24:50.80,Default,December,0,0,0,,So you're Nagisa-chan's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.42,0:24:54.02,Default,December,0,0,0,,You can call me December.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.77,0:24:55.80,Default,December,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.30,0:25:05.32,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.30,0:25:06.55,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Kojou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.42,0:25:15.82,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You're... Avrora...?
